000">It will be picked up on Monday at 3:00 pm since we are close on a Sunday.</font></span><span style="font-size: 15px; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: Arial;"><br></span></div><div><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Calibri; font-size: 15px; white-space: pre-wrap;">7.</span><span times="" new="" roman";"="" style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 10px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Calibri; font-size: 15px; white-space: pre-wrap;">How can I track the status of my shipment? </span><span style="font-size: 15px; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: Arial;"><font color="#000000">You may check the status of your cargo in our website: cargoking.com.ph. Just type your HAWB Tracking Number.</font></span><span style="font-size: 15px; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: Arial;"><br></span></div><div><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Calibri; font-size: 15px; white-space: pre-wrap;">8.    How do i file for my loss/damage cargo? </span><span style="font-size: 15px; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: Arial;"><font color="#000000">For claims of loss/damage cargo, you may call the number of the concerned Branch Supervisor.</font></span><span style="font-size: 15px; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: Arial;"><br></span></div><div><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Calibri; font-size: 15px; white-space: pre-wrap;">9.    Is Cargo King open for Franchise? </span><span style="font-size: 15px; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: Arial;"><font color="#000000">Yes. You may call our Sales and Operations Team at 0917 794 9296/0917 321 7410 for inquiries.</font></span></div>